[B]Do NOT do the client-side part if you are NOT doing Step 2. b)![/B]

Open your cache with Tom's Cache Suite, go into [CODE]Image Archives[/CODE] and then go to [CODE]Media[/CODE] Go into and edit both [CODE]28[/CODE] in [CODE]magicon2[/CODE] and [CODE]magicoff2[/CODE] Replace both with this:

